title: Howard Stern - Sept 29, 2014 [ALL-VERSIONS]
description:
Howard Stern - Sept 29, 2014

* Eric The Actor Tributes And Clips. 6:00am
* George Clooney's Wife. 6:15am
* Johnny Fratto Calls In About Eric The Actor's Wake. 6:30am
* This Date In Howard Stern History. 6:35am
* Odd Staff Stories With JD, Sal, Richard, Scott And Gary. 6:45am
* Howard's Weekend As A Bachelor. 7:20am
* The Beetlejuice Song Game. 7:30am
* Beetlejuice Visits. 7:50am
* Joey Boots' Podcast And Other Audio Clips. 8:55am
* Wynn And Jen Sit In For The News. 9:05am
* Robin's News. 9:15am
* Wrap Up Show - Wack Pack Poll, Sal And JD. 10:30am
* Wrap Up Show - Beetlejuice. 11:50am
* Wrap Up Show - Joy Riding In Stolen Cars. 11:10am

This includes an audio edit using @SternGeek's source.

1) This audio has been dyson compressed at 80% and amplified for maximum range.
Talk Radio & Podcasts sound much better, especially thru earbuds, with this edit.
You will also find it easier to hear audio details in loud environments.
If you have good speakers, or listen in a quite environment, you don't need this.

2) This encode will also use much less power from your batteries.

3) I have been experimenting lately with mixing in a small amount of white noise
in the final rendering to get rid of those awkward silences that the MP3 format
sometimes creates when there's not enough volume to compress.

4) I now include any Instagram pics/vids talked about during the show.
